{"tid":1266410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應處理遊行集會有否要求內地協助　警方：good idea！","createTime":"2019-06-29T14:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T15:26:56.000Z","uid":219244,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"791100a693cfadda763aa73dbc205045cbc7555f","tid":1266410,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"警方公布七一升旗禮及遊行集會安排。有外國傳媒問到，處理最近遊行集會活動時，警方有否要求其他地方的資源，包括來自內地的協助。中區警區副指揮官辛子健以英文回答時形容這是「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好主意</span></strong>」(<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>It is a good idea</strong></span>)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但否認有香港以外的人員協助警方。<br />\n<br />\n辛子健隨後以廣東話回應時解釋，他第一次聽到有關建議，認為是好意見，但好的意見未必一定要實行，重申目前警方沒有要求外援，至於日後是否需要，他說屬假設問題，不能回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zy6RmbY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZy6RmbY.png&h=275de2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2637302023044504?s=100000386042077&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F2637302023044504%3Fs%3D100000386042077%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=35dd3feb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2637302023044504?s=100000386042077&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢咩ranking呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連盧蛇都未出聲，佢一個中區副指揮官、高級警司，都可以話good idea?<br />\n<br />\n仲要比記者用廣東話問點解係好意見嘅時候口啞啞答「咁<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我哋係open minded架嘛，我哋開放式思維，咁先至希望有啲進步...咁記者朋友提呢個意見呢...因為我第一次聽呀...所以覺得係一個好嘅意見</strong></span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋外國記者都唔係比意見，明明係一條問題，佢on99屈人哋係比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cf63545bf3b38cd249de9022743d660987abd6","tid":1266410,"uid":219244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜而家啲警司咁低質素<br />\n<br />\n人哋問英文，佢仲未諗好答案就醒一句it is a good idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDse小組討論咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講中文又1999，吞吞吐吐丶邏輯不清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋問佢問題變咗比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次聽所以就係好意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca75368f7c922750a98bd0865cacc1e7c6346087","tid":1266410,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"連rthk記者都唔知點幫佢兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n段新聞點寫應該諗左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9a3af7b21e9243e3d48d9375ce55f6b6c22972","tid":1266410,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3c298137029bf5c0810db2e8b6212cfdfdfd49","tid":1266410,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我哋現階段，由頭到尾無諗過有呢個需要，至於日後會唔會？假設性問題，我答你唔到」<br />\n<br />\n即係唔排除叫公安落嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33552e67b5e931c9ccb77b979bd0cb20465f12c","tid":1266410,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96565232cc2aebe4274955d077f666fbc76e7622","tid":1266410,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}